node.text:
The most affected region by Coronavirus in Italy 💔 Lombardia is located in the center of Italy and Europe. Home to a variety of industries such as agriculture, manufacturing, fashion and eco-tourism. ⠀

The breathtaking landscape of Lombardy is a mixture of hills, mountains, lakes and plains. Its Alpine area is very popular in winter by skiers. Nature lovers are greeted by beautiful shoreline along the great Lombard lakes: Lake Garda, Lake Como, Lake Maggiore and Lake Iseo. ⠀

Stay strong Italy! 💚🤍❤️ #ForzaItalia

Video by @idressitalian ⠀

Always #wondermore

Visit: https://wonderlustcollective.co
